text.section:
As used in this section, unless the context requires otherwise:
"Authority" means the Kentucky Economic Development Finance Authority as created pursuant to KRS 154.20-010;
"Investor" has the same meaning as set forth in KRS 154.20-254;
"Investment fund" has the same meaning as set forth in KRS 154.20-254;
"Investment fund manager" has the same meaning as set forth in KRS 154.20-254; and
"Tax credit" means the credits provided for in KRS 154.20-258.
